title: Grateful Dead Live at Boston Garden on 1994-10-01
lineage: MAD > Sony TC-D8 > Optical out > Edirol FA-66 > Wavelab 1648 > R8Brain > CD-Wave > TLH > FLAC 1644 tagged. Recording & transfer by Andrew F. 02/2015
description:
Set 1

Help On The Way-> Slipknot!-> Franklin's Tower, Walkin' Blues, Althea, Me & My Uncle*-> Big River*, Just Like Tom Thumb's Blues, So Many Roads, Promised Land

Set 2

Scarlet Begonias-> Fire On The Mountain, Way To Go Home, Saint of Circumstance-> Terrapin Station-> Drums-> Space-> The Last Time-> Stella Blue-> One More Saturday Night E: Liberty

* Weir on acoustic guitar

reviews.review_text: I can't believe how good these sound who thought Nak300s could sound better than all the other super spendy microphones that taped this show?   Seriously, give them all a listen, this is the best!  Thanks Andrew F!
